## How it works
I ask you enough questions to understand your situation — and no more.
I negotiate with insurance companies on the spot to get you the best prices.
I show you instant quotes from trusted brands. Money (and time) in the bank!
If you’re looking for a catch, you won’t find one. It really is that simple.
